snippet.title: City of the Shroud Kickstarter
snippet.description:
City of the Shroud is on Kickstarter and raised 80% in the first 3 days! Back the campaign and get early access on Steam once the campaign is over!

Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/abyssalarts/city-of-the-shroud

Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/abyssalarts
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/abyssalarts
Website: https://www.abyssalarts.com
